---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Disclaimer" description="ToolMixr disclaimer - all tool results are for reference only and do not constitute professional advice.">

  <div class="legal-page">
    <h1>Disclaimer</h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated: May 2026</p>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>General Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>The tools and information provided on ToolMixr (toolmixr.com) are for general informational and educational purposes only. All results generated by our tools are for reference only and should not be used as a substitute for professional advice. We make no guarantees about the completeness, accuracy, reliability, or suitability of the information or tool outputs. Any reliance you place on such information is strictly at your own risk.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>Financial Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>The financial tools available on ToolMixr — including the Mortgage Calculator, ROI Calculator, Compound Interest Calculator, Loan Calculator, AdSense Revenue Calculator, Crypto Profit Calculator, Discount Calculator, Tip Calculator, and Percentage Calculator — are provided for estimation and educational purposes only. The results produced by these tools do <strong>not</strong> constitute financial, investment, tax, or legal advice.</p>
      <p>Financial decisions should be made in consultation with a qualified financial advisor, accountant, or other licensed professional. Market conditions, interest rates, tax laws, and other financial factors are subject to rapid change, and the figures generated by our calculators may not reflect current or actual conditions. ToolMixr is not responsible for any financial losses or decisions made based on the output of these tools.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>Health Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>The BMI Calculator on ToolMixr is provided for general informational purposes only and does <strong>not</strong> constitute medical, health, or nutritional advice. BMI is a simplistic measurement and does not account for factors such as muscle mass, bone density, age, sex, or overall health condition.</p>
      <p>Always consult a qualified healthcare professional before making any changes to your diet, exercise routine, or health regimen. Do not disregard professional medical advice or delay seeking it because of information provided by this tool.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
      <p>Some links on ToolMixr may be affiliate links. This means that if you click on a link and make a purchase or sign up for a service, we may receive a small commission at no additional cost to you. These commissions help us maintain and improve the site. We only recommend products and services that we believe may be useful to our users. Our editorial content is not influenced by affiliate partnerships.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>Accuracy Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>While we strive to ensure the accuracy of all tool outputs, ToolMixr cannot guarantee that results are error-free. Calculations and conversions may be affected by rounding, data precision limitations, or algorithmic approximations. Users should verify important results independently before relying on them for critical decisions.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>Changes to This Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>We reserve the right to modify or update this disclaimer at any time without prior notice. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date. Your continued use of ToolMixr after any changes constitutes acceptance of the revised disclaimer.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions about this disclaimer, please contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@toolmixr.com">contact@toolmixr.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page { padding: 40px 0 80px; max-width: 720px; }
  .legal-page h1 { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .legal-page .updated { color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 40px; font-size: 14px; }
  .legal-section { margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .legal-section h2 { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .legal-section p { color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .legal-section ul { color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; padding-left: 24px; }
  .legal-section ul li { margin-bottom: 6px; }
</style>
